THE PSL has seen some incredible weddings in recent times with some of the biggest stars marrying their loved ones including coaches. It was no different for well-travelled coach Joel Masutha who looked the part at his glamorous wedding. After 20-years of romance, the Pretoria Callies coach and his fiancée Sharon finally tied the knot this past weekend. The event was attended by close friends and family in Louis Trichardt, Limpopo on Saturday. The former Black Leopards, Chippa United and TTM coach said his 'I do’s' in fine fashion in a dazzling affair. Check it out... 